name: Ms-edge-youtube-auto-refresher
body:
### Welcome to MS EDGE Youtube Refresher
This Project was made so you can refresh YouTube pages to listen to music WITHOUT clicking out of a game etc.

### Designer Friendly
You can build new things from it but be sure to copy any ones work

### Authors and Contributors
Creator @Jan200101

### Support
Having Issues or need help ?
Open up a Issue [HERE](https://github.com/Jan200101/MS-Edge-Youtube-Auto-Refresher/issues)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
